192
00:18:08,295 --> 00:18:09,545
Look, I don't know exactly
where this hospital is...

193
00:18:09,546 --> 00:18:11,547
Yeah, we'll find it.

194
00:18:11,548 --> 00:18:14,718
Sure. It's just...

195
