207
00:19:00,305 --> 00:19:02,390
I know you mean well.

208
00:19:02,391 --> 00:19:05,352
I know you wanna
protect me. You have.

209
00:19:06,770 --> 00:19:09,438
And when we're done,
we'll go wherever you want.

210
00:19:09,439 --> 00:19:12,733
Tommy's, sheep ranch,

211
00:19:12,734 --> 00:19:13,569
